reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Be careful plugging into Macbook Pro
reviews.reviewText: There is no label (markings) showing which way the connectors should be connected to a computer (or phone). If you inadvertently PUSH the drive into a Mac slot (apply force, and it's the wrong way) it's apparent that you could damage the Macbook Pro slot! Wife gave me a label to mark the correct connection. That's sort of sad. But, hey, you get what you pay for. And this is cheap as all get out. Just don't hook up incorrectly and ruin a 2,700.00 Macbook Pro USB connection slot!
